reviewText: This video is produced by "Trains Magazine"  This video has excellent narration. and tells the story of the Union Pacific being moved from Pomona, California to Cheyenne, Wyoming.  This journey is the start of the restoration project by the Union Pacific Steam Shop Crew, lead by Ed Dickens.
Great Video of a great locomotive.
